comment2.text=\r\n\ M\u00E9todo\ act()\ vazio.\r\n\ <p>\r\n\ Este\ ator\ n\u00E3o\ realiza\ a\u00E7\u00F5es\ autom\u00E1ticas\ no\ mundo\ do\ Greenfoot.\r\n\ </p>\r\n
